    Verse: 6
Tags:
  - Discipline
---
The man who refuses to submit to discipline is like a river that overflows
its banks, thereby destroying the means by which it could reach the
sea. ... Fortunately, it is not left entirely to us to discipline
ourselves. Life does it for us.
